    description:
      'Create a `sum()`, which makes following possible\n\n```js\nconst sum1 = sum(1);\nsum1(2) == 3; // true\nsum1(3) == 4; // true\nsum(1)(2)(3) == 6; // true\nsum(5)(-1)(2) == 6; // true\n```',
